Empty J2EE Seam 2.1.2 WebApp with Apache Maven 2 support. Netbeans support.

There is also a simple ant build.xml in the root directory for local deployment. Please adapt the properties if you want to use it.

The datasource lies in mbook-ear/src/main/resources/mbook-ds.xml and has to be manually copied to the deploy directory (or with the supplied ant build.xml) and the content has to be changed for your needs.

The EJB project holds a simple Entity Bean for testing purpose ant the authenticor from the seam-gen project.

Dependency management is used to administrate dependency versions of the project in the parent pom.xml.
